title: Andy Warhol Soup Can Candle—Pop Wood
description:
One of Andy Warhol’s (American, 1928–1987) most iconic images can now be yours in 3D! This quirky, colorful candle is made of glass and has its own signature scent, Pop Wood, a combination of fig leaf, cedar wood, incense and musk. Made in France. 

3 x 2 ¾ in. diam
